fields.text: be a fish or a lemon that can talk?
have a slightly boring long term relationship or several hot flings?
go to work naked every Thursday  without any explanation or be completely bald other than two thick strands of hair that protrude from below your eye balls?
spend the evening together reading a good book or hit the town together?
be with someone who never does the dishes or someone who snores every night?
only be able to greet people by saying "Hi, nice to wibble you" or never succesfully hit a high-five again?
be with someone who is a great cook or someone who can mix fancy cocktails?
have to speak in rhyme all the time or speak only in questions?
only be able to travel by heelies or by giraffe?
date a good friend or a stranger?
never stop being serious or never stop joking?
never stub your toe again or never bite your tongue?
go out to the pub or go out to a club?
be fluent in every language or be able to play every instrument well?
be the last peron left on Earth or the first person to arrive on Mars?
eat an apple shaped like a banana or a banana shaped like an apple?
have to video call at least 10 friends one on one every day or only be able to communicate remotely via letter?
spend a whole week on the beach or spend a whole week sight seeing?
